descriptionHtml:
These are presets for one of my favorite custom female characters (Miss.Kitty)

The bodyslide preset goes in the bodyslide presets folder...obviously.

As for the racemenu preset it goes in here (Data-SKSE-Plugins-CharGen-Presets)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This Character preset requires the following mods to work.

1.DartHairColors by Dart98Rock

2.New Mikan Eyes by nerune

3.ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii
&
4.RaceMenu by Expired6978...Duh
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
If you want your character to have the intended look then you will also need
these (Recomended) Mods.

1.Wild Girl Skin (Skyrim Edition) by ME(Dibz420)

2.DiaperLoversSkyrim by Lucia1 (on Loverslab.com (For the Pacifire(s)

3.Whiskers by Quinn Winters
& last but not least
4.HDT Tails Wearable by deadzone45

-------------------------------------------------------
Yall Enjoy :P
